# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# │       │         │
# │       │         └─> Summary in present tense. Not capitalized. No period at the end.
# │       │
# │       └─> Scope: cogni|planner|gateway|session|task|approval|storage|sdk|ui|api|cli|deps|ci
# │
# └─> Type: feat|fix|refactor|perf|test|docs|style|chore

# [optional body]
# Explain *what* and *why* (not *how*). Wrap at 72 characters.

# [optional footer]
# Reference issues: Closes #123, Refs #456
# Breaking changes: BREAKING CHANGE: description

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Commit Type Guide / 提交类型指南
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# feat:     New user-facing feature / 新功能
#           ✓ Add new capability, API, component
#           ✗ NOT for improvements to existing features
#
# fix:      Bug fix / 错误修复
#           ✓ Correct incorrect behavior, crashes, data issues
#           ✗ NOT for code cleanup or refactoring
#
# refactor: Code restructuring without behavior change / 代码重构
#           ✓ Extract interfaces, rename, consolidate, reorganize
#           ✓ Improve code quality, readability, architecture
#           ✗ NOT for new features or bug fixes
#
# perf:     Performance improvement / 性能优化
#           ✓ Improve speed, memory, latency
#           ✗ NOT for functional changes
#
# test:     Add or update tests / 测试
#           ✓ Test-only changes
#           ✗ NOT for production code changes
#
# docs:     Documentation only / 文档
#           ✓ README, guides, comments, API docs
#
# style:    Formatting, whitespace / 代码风格
#           ✓ No logic changes
#
# chore:    Build, dependencies, tooling / 维护
#           ✓ No production code changes
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Examples / 示例
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# feat(cogni): add reflective learning loop
# fix(planner): prevent nil pointer in context assembly
# refactor(planner): extract runtime boundary interface
# perf(kernel): optimize event dispatch with batching
# test(approval): add evaluator edge case tests
# docs(sdk): update TypeScript SDK installation guide
# style(planner): fix indentation in context service
# chore(deps): upgrade go to 1.22
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Common Mistakes / 常见错误
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# ❌ feat(planner): use local service handles
# ✅ refactor(planner): use local service handles
#    → No new functionality, just internal improvement
#
# ❌ fix(ui): add Pack status grouping
# ✅ feat(ui): add Pack status grouping
#    → Adding new functionality, not fixing a bug
#
# ❌ feat(planner): add caching and fix race condition
# ✅ Split into two commits:
#    feat(planner): add prompt template caching
#    fix(planner): resolve context assembly race condition
#    → One purpose per commit
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Goal / 目标: Achieve 4:2:1 ratio (feat:fix:refactor) over next 30 days
# 目标：在未来 30 天内达到 4:2:1 的比例（feat:fix:refactor）
#
# Check distribution: node scripts/check-commit-type.mjs
# Full guide: docs/COMMIT-CONVENTIONS.md
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
